{"text_id":245072,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," present"," a"," lattice"," Boltzmann"," inverse"," kinetic"," approach"," for"," the"," simulation"," of"," incomp","ressible"," fluid"," flows"," governed"," by"," the"," Nav","ier","-","Stokes"," equations","."," The"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," stems"," from"," the"," limitations"," of"," traditional"," numerical"," methods"," in"," capturing"," complex"," fluid"," dynamics",","," such"," as"," turbulence",","," without"," sacrificing"," accuracy"," or"," computational"," efficiency","."," The"," key"," idea"," behind"," our"," approach"," is"," to"," interpret"," the"," inverse"," kinetic"," equation"," of"," the"," Boltzmann"," equation"," as"," a"," relaxation"," process"," that"," drives"," the"," system"," towards"," equilibrium",","," leading"," to"," a"," natural"," extension"," of"," the"," lattice"," Boltzmann"," method","."," ","\n\n","The"," methodology"," involves"," the"," discretization"," of"," the"," velocity"," distribution"," function"," in"," the"," physical"," domain"," and"," the"," use"," of"," a"," local"," streaming"," and"," collision"," procedure"," to"," update"," the"," distribution"," function"," at"," each"," lattice"," point","."," The"," macroscopic"," variables"," are"," then"," extracted"," from"," the"," moments"," of"," the"," distribution"," function","."," We"," demonstrate"," the"," validity"," and"," accuracy"," of"," our"," method"," by"," carrying"," out"," simulations"," of"," ","2","D"," and"," ","3","D"," lid","-","driven"," cavity"," flows"," at"," various"," Reynolds"," numbers",","," comparing"," our"," results"," with"," those"," obtained"," from"," existing"," numerical"," methods","."," ","\n\n","Our"," numerical"," experiments"," demonstrate"," that"," our"," lattice"," Boltzmann"," inverse"," kinetic"," approach"," is"," capable"," of"," accurately"," simulating"," complex"," incomp","ressible"," fluid"," flows",","," while"," also"," being"," computationally"," efficient","."," We"," find"," that"," our"," simulations"," show"," good"," agreement"," with"," experimental"," data",","," and"," our"," approach"," shows"," potential"," for"," further"," extension"," to"," more"," complex"," fluid"," systems"," and"," dynamics","."," Overall",","," our"," method"," represents"," a"," promising"," next"," step"," in"," the"," development"," of"," numerical"," methods"," for"," simulating"," complex"," fluid"," flows","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}